# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Square payments (food-truck online card checkout)
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your Square credentials.
# Get them from the Square Developer dashboard: https://developer.squareup.com/apps
#
# Start in SANDBOX to test with Square's test cards, then switch to
# production by changing *_ENV to "production" and using your live keys.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# --- Client (browser) — Web Payments SDK ---
# Safe to expose; these only render the card form.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SQUARE_APP_ID=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SQUARE_LOCATION_ID=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SQUARE_ENV=sandbox

# --- Server (secret) — Payments API ---
# NEVER expose the access token to the browser.
SQUARE_ACCESS_TOKEN=
SQUARE_LOCATION_ID=
SQUARE_ENV=sandbox

# Notes:
# - APP_ID:        Square app "Application ID" (sandbox or production).
# - LOCATION_ID:   same value can be used for both NEXT_PUBLIC_ and server vars.
# - ACCESS_TOKEN:  the matching sandbox/production access token (server only).
# - Until these are set, the cart shows the "Order on WhatsApp" option only;
#   the card-payment button appears once NEXT_PUBLIC_SQUARE_APP_ID + _LOCATION_ID exist.
# - Sandbox test card: 4111 1111 1111 1111, any future expiry, CVV 111, ZIP 94103.
